ice Hours</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>10:00 am to 07:30 pm</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Address</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>223 Bir Uttam Mir Shawkat Sarak, Dhaka-1208.</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Phone</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>+88-031-2515765</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Email</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>maximcardhaka@gmail.com</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Social Media Link</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>https://www.facebook.com/MaximCarDhaka/</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Website Link</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>http://www.maximcarcentre.com/Home</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c805c1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0c805c1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">08. MG Bangladesh</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f088b5f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f088b5f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>MG\r\n Bangladesh is not just a car dealer. They are a British automotive \r\ncompany that has been in the automobile industry since 1924. &nbsp;The \r\ncompany is the official partner of RANCON which sells and distributes \r\ncars throughout all districts in Bangladesh. MG Bangladesh has five \r\nshowrooms in Bangladesh, including Dhaka, Chittagong, Khulna, and \r\nBogura. They currently sell three models of MG cars in Bangladesh, \r\nincluding MG5, MG ZST, and MG HS. These vehicles have good value, \r\nstyling, and fuel efficiency.</p><table width=\"546\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Office Hours</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>09:00 am to 08:00 pm</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Address</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>215 Bir Uttam Mir Shawkat Sarak, Dhaka-1208</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Phone</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>+880 9617-454545</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Email</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>mgbangladeshtt@gmail.com</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Social Media Link</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><p>https://www.facebook.com/mgbangladesh/about</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"132\"><p><strong>Website Link</strong></p></td><td width=\"414\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"6FdvxvsupK\"><a href=\"https://mgmotor.com.bd/\">Home</a></blockquote></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d9a387 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4d9a387\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What Factors Affect The Growth of Car Showrooms In Bangladesh?</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-055973c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"055973c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>The number of car showrooms in Bangladesh is increasing day by day. Many factors contribute to this amazing growth.</p><h3><strong>Economic Growth</strong>:</h3><p>The\r\n average annual GDP growth rate of Bangladesh is 5.87%. Due to the \r\ngradual rise in income level, overall private vehicle ownerships \r\nincrease. More number of people are buying personal cars.</p><h3><strong>Urbanization</strong>:</h3><p>Urbanized\r\n areas have more people due to high job prospects. &nbsp;Congestion, traffic \r\njams, and pollution are more common in cities. Hence, people prefer to \r\nown and use private vehicles to save their time.</p><h3><strong>Changing Lifestyles</strong>:</h3><p>Owning\r\n a car in a developing country like Bangladesh is considered the \r\nultimate status symbol. Your financial standing and personal style are \r\noften reflected in the car you own.</p><p><strong>Wide Variety of Options</strong>:</p><p>Now,\r\n people have options to choose cars from various brands. Many \r\ninternational brands are even keen to invest in Bangladesh. This leads \r\nto a rise in the number of car showrooms in Bangladesh.</p><h3><strong>Financing Options</strong>:</h3><p>Many\r\n car dealer companies sell vehicles through loans. This increases the \r\ndemand for owning personal vehicles. Some car business organizations \r\noffer 5 years or more car loans. You just need to clear a small \r\nproportion of the downpayment.&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Technological Advancements</strong>:</h3><p>More\r\n exciting innovations are added to the automobile industry every year.&nbsp; \r\nThe future of cars will be electric, autonomous, and connected through \r\ndigital technology. It will increase the demand for new cars and more \r\nshowrooms will be opened.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dae481e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"dae481e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What are The Challenges for Future Car Showrooms?</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f8b841c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f8b841c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>Though the prospects for new car showrooms are flourishing, there are still some challenges.</p><h3><strong>Infrastructure</strong>:</h3><p>Better\r\n transportation infrastructure is a must to increase the demand for \r\nowning personal vehicles. The government should take steps to fund \r\nhighways, roads, and parking lots. Otherwise, it will affect the market \r\ndemand for cars.</p><h3><strong>Environmental Issues</strong>:</h3><p>The\r\n air pollution level of Bangladesh is not up to mark compared to \r\ndeveloped countries. One of the best solutions is using electric \r\nvehicles. This will cause minimal impact on environmental pollution.</p><h3><strong>Regulations and Taxes</strong>:</h3><p>The\r\n import tax of a car is at least 200%. It can be as high as 350% \r\ndepending on the brand and engine capacity. Plus, Bangladesh car import \r\nrules and vehicular-emission standards will directly or indirectly \r\naffect car ownership decisions.</p><h3><strong>After-Sales Service</strong>:</h3><p>It\r\n is necessary to provide warranty and after-sales services to ensure \r\nbetter customer satisfaction. This will build loyal customers and help \r\nbrands to grow their business.</p></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7997638 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7997638\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10e95bd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"10e95bd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>As\r\n a conscious car enthusiast, you must choose a reliable car showroom in \r\nBangladesh to get a quality vehicle at the best price. We have already \r\nmentioned the 8 best car dealers to choose a reliable personal car based\r\n on your budget. You can buy new or reconditioned vehicles depending on \r\nhow much you want to pay. Car Theory BD is one of the best choices for \r\nbuying affordable Japanese cars at an attractive price. &nbsp;</p></div></div